      "text": [
        " يُكْرَهُ الْمُفْدَمُ إِلَّا لِلْعَرُوسِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from a man, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘The vibrant-coloured (clothing) is disliked except for the wedding’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from a man who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Wearing clothes of sharp color is not desirable except for weddings/” "
        ]
      }
